{"tid":2036901,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中共係咪唔知道「義勇軍進行曲」嘅歷史原義係咩？","createTime":"2020-05-26T17:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T18:52:32.000Z","uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71c6dad54ab72a1402605164ab1427f090e07274","tid":2036901,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:33:07.000Z","msg":"中共強行立完國歌法實後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔講首歌嘅歷史...<br />\n以香港人嘅變通機智，國歌法實比人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打蛇隨棍上</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如連登仔已經諗緊點「騎劫」鄰國國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似瘋狂重溫作詞人作曲人生平咁，國歌法一定保護<br />\n用真正嘅「進行曲」黎抗爭，國歌法又保護<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我堅毅 我奮進<br />\n中共係咪唔知咩係「義勇軍進行曲」？</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1935年，該曲由田漢作詞、聶耳作曲。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1966年文化大革命爆發，田漢被批鬥，1968年受迫害致死，1975年被宣佈為「叛徒」，被「永遠開除黨籍」，所以正式演奏改為「有曲無詞」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n1949年11月15日，《人民日報》發表了關於國旗、國歌和年號「新華社答讀者問」：「《義勇軍進行曲》是十餘年來在中國廣大人民的鬥爭中最流行的歌曲，已經具有歷史意義。採用《義勇軍進行曲》為中華人民共和國現時的國歌而不加修改，是為了喚起人民回想祖國創造過程中的艱難憂患，鼓舞人民發揚反抗帝國主義侵略的愛國熱情，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">把革命進行到底。</span></span></strong>這與蘇聯人民曾長期以《國際歌》為國歌，法國人民今天仍以《馬賽曲》為國歌的作用是一樣的。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文化大革命期間的義勇軍進行曲<br />\n《義勇軍進行曲》作為國歌唱了17年。在1966年開始的<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「文化大革命」中，田漢被打成「右派」，於1968年含冤去世。</span></span></strong>其作品亦被認為有「政治問題」，所以禁止演唱用田漢作詞的《義勇軍進行曲》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8S1xFx7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8S1xFx7.jpg&h=e5cb3076&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87d2e8758731a52a9019a5a0980ce605209cefb8","tid":2036901,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UOyjchZjK1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUOyjchZjK1U&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=e5c5b8c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UOyjchZjK1U</a>"},{"pid":"8ee8c1042a04d7da220f9d7754ff21d19cf61932","tid":2036901,"uid":115988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"【527金鐘？】每次盲目複製成功抗爭經驗，都慘敗收場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036949</a>"},{"pid":"2aa350fcb419b70271edf058bd8a24f4fb970db1","tid":2036901,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:44:11.000Z","msg":"我記得聶耳都係差唔多"},{"pid":"4783ae415442146434074158e9caca906a317d96","tid":2036901,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:52:32.000Z","msg":"變通機智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />指比人點去送頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}